data.description: Bring all your toys!!! A light and bright, remodeled in 2019, 1649 sq. ft. manufactured home has 3 bedroom, 2 bathrooms and sits on a little over an acre.  The detached two car garage has a small workshop.  The property also has an RV hookup and plenty of room to store all your off-road toys.  This is a great property in which to expand on your creative home dreams!!
